Add property "pinctrl-names" to swap pin mode between gpio and dpi mode. Set
the dpi pins to gpio mode and output-low to avoid leakage current when dpi
disabled.

Signed-off-by: Jitao Shi <jitao.shi@mediatek.com>
---
